data.description: This one shines!!! This one has a very private backyard, firepit, covered deck all on a lot that is almost an acre and that's just the outside. Inside you'll find a kitchen with stainless steel appliances, 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths and a main level laundry room. There is also a full unfinished basement for storage or future growth. Don't let this one slip away!!!
